name: Scene Precede
description: Genesis Period. 2021 Oct #001. My work is about the human desire to advance and make progress. The meaning of the title is that it is about the prelude to such a desired advancement, as such there is a lot of uncertainty as to what the outcome will be. I was inspired by nature and I thought it would be nice to take the people away from the city and let them see how nature really looks like. It would give them a feeling of detachment from their daily life and give them time to reflect about who they are and what their role is in the scene we all live in. Botto in conversation with GPT-3.
